---
title: Curried Jamaican Beef & Collard Greens with Spicy Red Chili & Creamy Polenta
description: This unique stir-fry dish brings the flavors of Jamaican beef patties to you in a simple, no-fuss recipe. Mustardy turmeric and curry powder build layers of flavor along with hot chili pepper and pungent garlic. Earthy collards offer the perfect counterpoint to these highly aromatic flavors.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55560f954dab71fb718b4567.
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/55560f954dab71fb718b4567.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/curried-jamaican-beef-collard-greens-55560f954dab71fb718b4567
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 601 kcal
